snippet.title: Paramount Plus
snippet.description:
Paramount+ is here! 

With Paramount+ you can stream over 30,000 episodes & movies from CBS, BET, Comedy Central, MTV, Nickelodeon, Smithsonian Channel & Paramount Pictures including exclusive originals plus live sports & news.

Don’t miss out on the Paramount+ Originals collection—including exclusive shows and movies you’ll only catch here—like Kamp Koral: SpongeBob’s Under Years plus returning seasons of Why Women Kill, The Good Fight, and Star Trek: Picard.

Plus, you can count on Paramount+ for the most iconic movies, plus the latest in live sports and news with your local CBS station, CBSN, CBS Sports HQ and ET Live. 

Start your free trial now and start streaming! 
https://bit.ly/3kGGJmg
